data.description: Hello interested renters, here we have a beautiful & huge 2 bedroom apartment located in country club. This apartment is on the second floor of a private house & it provides hardwood floors, an eat in kitchen, massive living room, full size bath, & 2 large bedrooms with their own windows & closets. As far as utilities only heat & water is included. Sorry but pets are not allowed. Street parking is available & the neighborhood is nice & quiet. This unit will not last long. So hurry & call the realtor now.
